            <journal-aims-scope>
                <p>
                    <bold>Recent Patents and Topics on Imaging</bold> publishes review and research articles, and guest edited single-topic issues in the field of imaging including reviews on patents. It provides an important and reliable source of current information on developments in the field. The journal is essential reading for all researchers involved in the field of Imaging. Research areas covered by the journal are: cellular, molecular, digital and diagnostic imaging.</p>
